### Get Video Duration
# Get the total duration of a YouTube video
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/video/duration?youtubeUrl=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth.username}} {{basicAuth.password}}

###

### Get Video Duration - Short URL Format
# Test with youtu.be format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/video/duration?youtubeUrl=https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth.username}} {{basicAuth.password}}

